msgid "Going asynchronous"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/1.7/guides/amazon-ses.adoc:219
msgid "Thanks to the AWS SDK v2.x used by the Quarkus extension, you can use the asynchronous programming model out of the box."
